rows.label: qst201330_msg0002
rows.name:
How could a mere Blade stand
in the way of my plans?!

rows.label: qst201330_msg0003
rows.name:
I won't let it end here... I'll make
you sorely regret the day you made
an enemy of me!

rows.label: qst201330_msg0004
rows.name:
The port is right through there.
He must mean to escape by ship.

rows.label: qst201330_msg0005
rows.name:
Well, isn't that just like a villain.
I'm not about to let him get away!
